r a weeknight meal, it also makes a lovely dish for a dinner party or fancier holiday. You could make this for \u003c/span\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/recipes/holiday/easter/\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eEaster\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003cspan\u003e and serve it with \u003c/span\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/2016/01/howsweeteats-house-salad/\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003ea big salad\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003cspan\u003e and \u003c/span\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/2020/11/best-mashed-potatoes/\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003emashed\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003cspan\u003e or \u003c/span\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/2023/12/rosemary-melting-potatoes/\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003emelting potatoes\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003cspan\u003e. \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan id=\"more-98583\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/sticky-apricot-pork-tenderloin-13-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"sticky apricot pork tenderloin\" width=\"1749\" height=\"2200\" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt=\"\" data-jpibfi-post-url=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/2025/04/sticky-apricot-pork-tenderloin/\" data-jpibfi-post-title=\"Sticky Apricot Pork Tenderloin.\" data-jpibfi-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/sticky-apricot-pork-tenderloin-13-scaled.jpg\" srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/sticky-apricot-pork-tenderloin-13-scaled.jpg 1749w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/sticky-apricot-pork-tenderloin-13-728x916.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/sticky-apricot-pork-tenderloin-13-768x966.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/sticky-apricot-pork-tenderloin-13-1221x1536.jpg 1221w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/sticky-apricot-pork-tenderloin-13-1628x2048.jpg 1628w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/sticky-apricot-pork-tenderloin-13-150x189.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1749px) 100vw, 1749px\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%201749%202200\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/sticky-apricot-pork-tenderloin-13-scaled.jpg 1749w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/sticky-apricot-pork-tenderloin-13-728x916.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/sticky-apricot-pork-tenderloin-13-768x966.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/sticky-apricot-pork-tenderloin-13-1221x1536.jpg 1221w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/sticky-apricot-pork-tenderloin-13-1628x2048.jpg 1628w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/sticky-apricot-pork-tenderloin-13-150x189.jpg 150w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/sticky-apricot-pork-tenderloin-13-scaled.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eYou can also serve this with the \u003c/span\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/2025/03/pasta-chopped-salad/\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003epasta chopped salad\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003cspan\u003e for a great weeknight meal! It’s such a good complement and very satisfying. \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eFor leftovers, you can always do sliders or sandwiches. Add some slaw on top or even just lettuce and tomato! BBQ sauce and cheddar… there are so many ways to mix it up.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eI like to throw it on a baguette and top with some arugula and chimichurri. That is such a great way to repurpose the meal and make it seem extra special. \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/sticky-apricot-pork-tenderloin-10-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"sticky apricot pork tenderloin\" width=\"1700\" height=\"2200\" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt=\"\" data-jpibfi-post-url=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/2025/04/sticky-apricot-pork-tenderloin/\" data-jpibfi-post-title=\"Sticky Apricot Pork Tenderloin.\" data-jpibfi-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/sticky-apricot-pork-tenderloin-10-scaled.jpg\" srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/sticky-apricot-pork-tenderloin-10-scaled.jpg 1700w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/sticky-apricot-pork-tenderloin-10-728x942.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/sticky-apricot-pork-tenderloin-10-768x994.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/sticky-apricot-pork-tenderloin-10-1187x1536.jpg 1187w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/sticky-apricot-pork-tenderloin-10-1582x2048.jpg 1582w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/sticky-apricot-pork-tenderloin-10-150x194.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1700px) 100vw, 1700px\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%201700%202200\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/sticky-apricot-pork-tenderloin-10-scaled.jpg 1700w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/sticky-apricot-pork-tenderloin-10-728x942.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/sticky-apricot-pork-tenderloin-10-768x994.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/sticky-apricot-pork-tenderloin-10-1187x1536.jpg 1187w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/sticky-apricot-pork-tenderloin-10-1582x2048.jpg 1582w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/sticky-apricot-pork-tenderloin-10-150x194.jpg 150w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/sticky-apricot-pork-tenderloin-10-scaled.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eSometimes I will slice it very thin and serve it on salad. And other times, I will shred what is left and we will even use it for tacos. You could also make fried rice or throw it in pasta too! The apricot sauce is fairly neutral and works will with just about anything. \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eIt’s a dish to make over and over again!\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/sticky-apricot-pork-tenderloin-12-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"sticky apricot pork tenderloin\" width=\"1664\" height=\"2200\" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt=\"\" data-jpibfi-post-url=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/2025/04/sticky-apricot-pork-tenderloin/\" data-jpibfi-post-title=\"Sticky Apricot Pork Tenderloin.\" data-jpibfi-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/sticky-apricot-pork-tenderloin-12-scaled.jpg\" srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/sticky-apricot-pork-tenderloin-12-scaled.jpg 1664w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/sticky-apricot-pork-tenderloin-12-728x963.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/sticky-apricot-pork-tenderloin-12-768x1015.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/sticky-apricot-pork-tenderloin-12-1162x1536.jpg 1162w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/sticky-apricot-pork-tenderloin-12-1549x2048.jpg 1549w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/sticky-apricot-pork-tenderloin-12-150x198.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1664px) 100vw, 1664px\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%201664%202200\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/sticky-apricot-pork-tenderloin-12-scaled.jpg 1664w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/sticky-apricot-pork-tenderloin-12-728x963.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/sticky-apricot-pork-tenderloin-12-768x1015.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/sticky-apricot-pork-tenderloin-12-1162x1536.jpg 1162w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/sticky-apricot-pork-tenderloin-12-1549x2048.jpg 1549w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/sticky-apricot-pork-tenderloin-12-150x198.jpg 150w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/sticky-apricot-pork-tenderloin-12-scaled.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003ch2\u003eSticky Apricot Pork Tenderloin\u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cdiv id=\"wprm-recipe-container-98598\" data-recipe-id=\"98598\" data-servings=\"4\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/sticky-apricot-pork-tenderloin-9-250x250.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/sticky-apricot-pork-tenderloin-9-250x250.jpg 250w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/sticky-apricot-pork-tenderloin-9-500x500.jpg 500w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/sticky-apricot-pork-tenderloin-9-336x336.jpg 336w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/sticky-apricot-pork-tenderloin-9-672x672.jpg 672w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/sticky-apricot-pork-tenderloin-9-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/sticky-apricot-pork-tenderloin-9-300x300.jpg 300w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/sticky-apricot-pork-tenderloin-9-96x96.jpg 96w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 200px) 100vw, 200px\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%20200%20200\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/sticky-apricot-pork-tenderloin-9-250x250.jpg 250w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/sticky-apricot-pork-tenderloin-9-500x500.jpg 500w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/sticky-apricot-pork-tenderloin-9-336x336.jpg 336w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/sticky-apricot-pork-tenderloin-9-672x672.jpg 672w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/sticky-apricot-pork-tenderloin-9-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/sticky-apricot-pork-tenderloin-9-300x300.jpg 300w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/sticky-apricot-pork-tenderloin-9-96x96.jpg 96w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/sticky-apricot-pork-tenderloin-9-250x250.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003ch2\u003eSticky Apricot Pork Tenderloin\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eWe love this sticky apricot pork tenderloin! It\u0026#39;s so tender and juicy, topped with a sticky apricot sauce and packed with flavor. Perfect to serve on a weeknight or even a fancy holiday. Goes with just about any side!\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\u003cdiv data-recipe=\"98598\" data-servings=\"4\"\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"0\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e2\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003epounds\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.target.com/p/all-natural-pork-tenderloin-price-per-lb-good-38-gather-8482/-/A-82166518?aflt=plt\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"\u003epork tenderloin,\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003e(this is usually 2 filets) \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003ekosher salt and pepper\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"2\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e1\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003eteaspoon\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.target.com/p/garlic-powder-3-12oz-good-38-gather-8482/-/A-77585075?aflt=plt\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"\u003egarlic powder\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"3\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e1\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003eteaspoon\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.target.com/p/smoked-spanish-paprika-2-12oz-good-38-gather-8482/-/A-84669679?aflt=plt\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"\u003esmoked paprika\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"4\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e1\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003e(13 ounce)\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003ejar apricot preserves\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"5\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e¼\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003ecup\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003ewater\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\n\u003cdiv data-recipe=\"98598\"\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli id=\"wprm-recipe-98598-step-0-0\"\u003e\u003cp\u003ePreheat the oven to 400 degrees F.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli id=\"wprm-recipe-98598-step-0-1\"\u003e\u003cp\u003ePat the pork tenderloin dry with a paper towel. Season it all over liberally with salt and pepper. Season it with garlic powder and smoked paprika.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli id=\"wprm-recipe-98598-step-0-2\"\u003e\u003cp\u003eHeat the olive oil in a cast iron skillet over medium-high heat. Add the tenderloin and seared on all sides until deeply golden brown.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli id=\"wprm-recipe-98598-step-0-3\"\u003e\u003cp\u003eWhile searing, whisk together the preserves and water. Pour the mixture into the skillet and let it bubble up. Reduce it to the simmer and cook for 1 to 2 minutes.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli id=\"wprm-recipe-98598-step-0-4\"\u003e\u003cp\u003eTransfer the pan to the oven and roast for 15 minutes, then take the internal temperature. I like mine to be at at least 155 degrees F.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli id=\"wprm-recipe-98598-step-0-5\"\u003e\u003cp\u003eRemove the pan and let the pork rest for a few minutes. Spoon the apricot preserves in the pan over top to serve!\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCourse: \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003eMain Course\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCuisine: \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003eAmerican\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/sticky-apricot-pork-tenderloin-5-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"sticky apricot pork tenderloin\" width=\"1726\" height=\"2200\" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt=\"\" data-jpibfi-post-url=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/2025/04/sticky-apricot-pork-tenderloin/\" data-jpibfi-post-title=\"Sticky Apricot Pork Tenderloin.\" data-jpibfi-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/sticky-apricot-pork-tenderloin-5-scaled.jpg\" srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/sticky-apricot-pork-tenderloin-5-scaled.jpg 1726w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/sticky-apricot-pork-tenderloin-5-728x928.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/sticky-apricot-pork-tenderloin-5-768x979.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/sticky-apricot-pork-tenderloin-5-1205x1536.jpg 1205w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/sticky-apricot-pork-tenderloin-5-1606x2048.jpg 1606w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/sticky-apricot-pork-tenderloin-5-150x191.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1726px) 100vw, 1726px\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%201726%202200\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/w